ification"" use_icon=""on"" font_icon=""&#xe052;||divi||400"" icon_placement=""left"" image_icon_width=""20px"" content_max_width=""100%"" _builder_version=""4.23.4"" _module_preset=""default"" header_font=""|700|||||||"" header_font_size=""18px"" custom_css_main_element="".et_pb_blurb_description {||margin-left: -20px!important}"" custom_css_blurb_title=""margin-left: -20px;||margin-top: 1px;"" global_colors_info=""{}""]Our team will review your submission, verifying the details for accuracy and completeness.[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb title=""Confirmation and Follow-Up"" use_icon=""on"" font_icon=""&#xe052;||divi||400"" icon_placement=""left"" image_icon_width=""20px"" content_max_width=""100%"" _builder_version=""4.24.3"" _module_preset=""default"" header_font=""|700|||||||"" header_font_size=""18px"" custom_css_main_element="".et_pb_blurb_description {||margin-left: -20px!important}"" custom_css_blurb_title=""margin-left: -20px;||margin-top: 1px;"" global_colors_info=""{}""]<p>Après examen, nous vous contacterons avec une confirmation et les prochaines étapes, qu'il s'agisse de finaliser la revendication de votre annonce ou de vous guider tout au long du processus d'ajout à notre annuaire.</p>[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb title=""Broaden Your Professional Reach"" use_icon=""on"" font_icon=""&#xe052;||divi||400"" icon_placement=""left"" image_icon_width=""20px"" content_max_width=""100%"" _builder_version=""4.24.3"" _module_preset=""default"" header_font=""|700|||||||"" header_font_size=""18px"" custom_css_main_element="".et_pb_blurb_description {||margin-left: -20px!important}"" custom_css_blurb_title=""margin-left: -20px;||margin-top: 1px;"" global_colors_info=""{}""]Being part of our directory connects you with a wider client base, helping to extend your professional footprint and enhance your online visibility.[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_divider color=""RGBA(22,107,181,0.2)"" _builder_version=""4.24.3"" _module_preset=""default"" custom_margin=""10px||||false|false"" gl